<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-198] Cleanup pom, remove lib dependencies, etc.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-198</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This patch cleans up the poms to not do install.  It removes the core/lib directory.  I have published the necessary artifacts to our Mahout Maven repo already, so they should be publicly available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/MAHOUT/ThirdPartyDependencies&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/MAHOUT/ThirdPartyDependencies&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/6f026182150f0f50/dependencies_outside_maven_central_was_oh_joy&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/6f026182150f0f50/dependencies_outside_maven_central_was_oh_joy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
